org.apache.flink.runtime.io.network.netty

类 PartitionRequestClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.io.network.netty.PartitionRequestClient

  • public class PartitionRequestClient
extends java.lang.Object
    Partition request client for remote partition requests.

    This client is shared by all remote input channels, which request a partition from the same ConnectionID.

      • incrementReferenceCounter

        boolean incrementReferenceCounter()
        Increments the reference counter.

        Note: the reference counter has to be incremented before returning the instance of this client to ensure correct closing logic.

      • sendTaskEvent

        public void sendTaskEvent(ResultPartitionID partitionId,
                          TaskEvent event,
                          RemoteInputChannel inputChannel)
                   throws java.io.IOException
        Sends a task event backwards to an intermediate result partition producer.

        Backwards task events flow between readers and writers and therefore will only work when both are running at the same time, which is only guaranteed to be the case when both the respective producer and consumer task run pipelined.

        抛出:
        java.io.IOException
